@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@receiptId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@serviceOrderCode = 1
@userCode = 1

### Update receipt
### Keep serviceOrderCode coherent to avoid moving the receipt to another order by mistake
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/receipts/{{receiptId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "serviceOrderCode": "{{serviceOrderCode}}",
  "amount": 200.00,
  "paymentMethod": "CREDIT_CARD",
  "notes": "Pagamento ajustado",
  "receivedByCode": "{{userCode}}"
}
